    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293340/extras/cc26c381cb3ceef24ac0afd3efb0780f.poster.avif?t=1752754341\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293340/extras/cc26c381cb3ceef24ac0afd3efb0780f.webm?t=1752754341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293340/extras/cc26c381cb3ceef24ac0afd3efb0780f.mp4?t=1752754341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i><strong>Deadly Dealings</strong></i> is an intense <strong>multiplayer</strong> card game where strategy, deception, and timing determine the victor. Battle your friends in a mysterious, isolated arena suspended in an endless void, where every decision counts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a diverse deck of cards to attack, defend, and outmaneuver your opponents. The stakes are high—will you play conservatively, build your defenses, or go all-in for a decisive strike? With matches ranging from <strong>2 to 4 players</strong>, every game is an unpredictable clash of tactics and wits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Multiplayer Action</strong>: Play with 2 to 4 players in a battle of cunning and skill.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Deck Options</strong>: Utilize cards for attacking, shielding, upgrading, or merging to gain the upper hand.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Atmosphere</strong>: Compete in a surreal, nowhere-like arena with stunning visuals and dynamic lighting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engaging Visual Effects</strong>: Enjoy polished animations, glowing card highlights, and seamless interactions.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather your allies—or rivals—and step into <i>Deadly Dealings</i>, where every move could seal your fate or bring you victory<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293340/extras/d9102ea1f6f534e49a9d4ea812d9263f.poster.avif?t=1752754341\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293340/extras/d9102ea1f6f534e49a9d4ea812d9263f.webm?t=1752754341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293340/extras/d9102ea1f6f534e49a9d4ea812d9263f.mp4?t=1752754341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
